</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-35_ pf-text-1"><strong>Diversity</strong> - Embracing the differences among people, including but not limited to race, ethnicity, gender, sexual orientation, disability, and age.

































</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-37_ pf-text-1"><strong>Inclusion</strong> - Creating an environment where everyone feels valued, respected, and supported.


































