</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-46_ pf-text-1"><strong>The public sector equality duty </strong>- Requires public bodies to consider how their policies and decisions affect people with different protected characteristics and work towards eliminating discrimination.


































